Company Overview of Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC assembles sewing machines, and manufactures cabinets and stands for sewing machines in Sri Lanka. The company was incorporated in 1963 and is based in Ratmalana, Sri Lanka. Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC is a subsidiary of Singer (Sri Lanka) PLC.


No. 2, 5th LaneRatmalana,  Sri LankaFounded in 196386 Employees



Phone: 94 112 634 416

Fax: 94 112 637 766








Key Executives for Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC


Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC Key Developments

Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC Announces Demise of Dr. Saman Kelegama, the Non-Executive Chairman of the Company
Jun 27 17
The Board of Directors of Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC announced the demise of Dr. Saman Kelegama, the non-executive Chairman of the company on June 23, 2017.


Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC Reports Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 9 17
Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC reported earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported revenue of LKR 223,413,000 against LKR 263,107,000 a year ago. Profit before taxation was LKR 12,814,000 against LKR 13,443,000 a year ago. Profit for the quarter was LKR 9,394,000 against LKR 9,846,000 a year ago. Basic earnings per share were LKR 2.44 against LKR 2.56 a year ago. Finance Income was LKR 3,656,000 against LKR 1,860,000 a year ago. Net cash flows from operating activities were LKR 9,853,000 against LKR 31,770,000 a year ago.


Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC, Annual General Meeting, Mar 31, 2017
Mar 13 17
Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC, Annual General Meeting, Mar 31, 2017, at 11:00 Sri Lanka Standard Time. Location: Singer (Sri Lanka) PLC, No. 80, Nawam Mawatha, Colombo 2 Sri Lanka


